            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_0177tYQLjSuUjrrUmtg4CD9E\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I can see that the tracking library (L10) exists and is properly configured, but **none of the components with email capture forms are using it**. I found three components that need instrumentation:\\n\\n1. **Hero.tsx** - Has an email input and button but no form submission handler\\n2. **CTA.tsx** - Has an email input and button but no form submission handler  \\n3. **Pricing.tsx** - Has buttons but no email capture (this might be intentional for \\\"Contact Sales\\\")\\n\\nLet me fix the Hero and CTA components to properly use L10.createLead():\"},{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01RB1CNaPNbCqxLtzdZcy5bZ\",\"name\":\"write_file\",\"input\":{\"file_path\":\"/src/components/Hero.tsx\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"max_tokens\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":5,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":6092,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":10322,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":6092,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":2048,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
